# 复现论文：Exploring the Controlling Factors of Watershed 
# Streamflow Variability Using Hydrological and Machine Learning Models
# 对应期刊：Water Resources Research, 2025
# 作者：Ding et al.
# R语言实现：包含数据模拟、模型训练、SHAP分析、情景模拟与归因
